Sentencas: Hyper-coal, produced by the Kobe Steel Company, was investigated by analytical and physico-chemical methods to consider its potential usability as a fuel for a direct carbon fuel cell with solid oxide electrolyte (DC-SOFC).
Titulo: Use of ash-free Hyper-coal as a fuel for a direct carbon fuel cell with solid oxide electrolyte

Sentencas: The performed tests showed that DC-SOFCs fed with this processed fossil coal were characterized by stable operation with reasonable current and power densities.
Titulo: Use of ash-free Hyper-coal as a fuel for a direct carbon fuel cell with solid oxide electrolyte

Sentencas: The performance of the fuel cells can be improved by using iron as a catalyst for the anodic reaction and by the choice of appropriate working conditions.
Titulo: Use of ash-free Hyper-coal as a fuel for a direct carbon fuel cell with solid oxide electrolyte
